div.p:
                    Graves summarized SEATO needs as follows: 
                        1.

Improve backstopping by Foreign Offices;
                        2.

Strengthen representation Bangkok;
                        3.

Demonstrate we regard treaty as vital;
                        4.

Increase feeling among other Asian countries that treaty is essential
                            for preservation of area;
                        5.

Prepare report for Council which will show Asia and world what SEATO has done, is capable of doing and
                            will do.
